{"tid":707862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩今明兩天訪問北京","createTime":"2018-06-19T02:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T04:21:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c373c5bb588aa646ca808c459ba13219edfb44c2","tid":707862,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"央視新聞報道，今明兩天北韓領導人金正恩對中國進行訪問。據韓聯社報道，一架北韓專機今早從平壤飛往北京。日本媒體稱，北韓領導人金正恩拜訪中國國家主席習近平，報告上周的「特金會」事宜，這也將是金正恩第3度前往中國會見習近平。<br />\n據報，高麗航空JS-251次航班今天上午從平壤起飛，飛往北京。朝媒曾播出過北韓領導人金正恩親自駕駛同種機型的畫面，他在北韓境內視察時，也常乘坐該機。<br />\n另外，據《日本經濟新聞》報道，中國與北韓的消息人士指出，金正恩今日搭機前往北京，與習近平見面，報告早前與美國總統特朗普舉行會議事宜。目前中國與北韓的警備保安，已出現些微異動，顯示金正恩應該很有可能在今日前往北京。<br />\n報道也指，金正恩在特金會中向特朗普表達非核化的意願，以降低美方對北韓的制裁強度。金正恩此行晤習近平，應該就是要尋求習近平的支持，並討論未來中國與北韓的關係局勢走向。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180619/58335383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58335383&d=R0oyRw0%2F7CAxgVAVebxmzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d9e06159\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58335383&h=300ae3c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180619/58335383</a>"},{"pid":"319e62e626fbe4b7c1cb8abaca802252e3e5db73","tid":707862,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"金仔又去傾生意<br />\n地上最強八十後"},{"pid":"2ec1f6bf952875de3597c8b87b93b6a558ddb4d1","tid":707862,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38fd1b92720c58506f5ff3a49cfbe73f79a80ae3","tid":707862,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"咁遲先REPORT, 又拎金仔黎同美國講數"},{"pid":"ca378829716075d856791b859556eeacc3c8e006","tid":707862,"uid":13545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:59:27.000Z","msg":"世界仔"},{"pid":"518162c5ad4d4eb1513de10809450acb8da62021","tid":707862,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"肥金：係窮呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"737628e10201ba1d0ca66ef72b5ba6eabbde3026","tid":707862,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"金仔點會話得罪邊一方<br />\n自己國家窮<br />\n出過去讀書眼界唔同左<br />\n今次去中國點都係交際下<br />\n但講到金仔信邊個<br />\n唔通信小學雞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2490566f3c7e24f1d0c3e800e48a720e4a1d7e47","tid":707862,"uid":72725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"on9, JS251喺定期航班嚟"},{"pid":"6d2bf0980a4d61e9dc7dd04393a884646aa63269","tid":707862,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2490566f3c7e24f1d0c3e800e48a720e4a1d7e47","tid":707862,"uid":72725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"on9, JS251喺定期航班嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcfdee5ce55c7a75d3d4d15d564792fdd49739e","tid":707862,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122101_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122101_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif&h=f1d7e0a0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}